  "texts": [
    "A study about restaurant survival prediction (Li et al. 2023) categories customers' online review into five categories: location, tastiness, price, service, and atmosphere, by using pretrained language model (BERT) and aspect-based sentiment analysis.",
    "Their results show that aspect-based sentiment, compared to overall review sentiment, can improve the prediction performance of restaurant survival.",
    "In Ding et al. (2014), a series of events representing news articles and headlines are extracted as a tuple denoting an event which consists of three values (Action, Actor and Object).",
    "Based on the articles, three values are extracted which together become an event.",
    "For example in the headline \"Apple launches a new iPhone\" where Actor = \"Apple\", Action = \"Launches\" and Object = \"iPhone\"."
  ],
